window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From the award-winning and </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author of&nbsp;</b><b><i>The Rest of the Story</i></b><b> comes a powerful novel about loss, love, and moving on.</b></p> <p>Nothing is going as planned for Macy this summer.&nbsp;</p> <p>Not the job at Wish Catering, and definitely not Wes.</p> <p>But Macy soon discovers that the things you expect least are sometimes the things you need most.</p> <p><b>\"Dessen gracefully balances comedy with tragedy and introduces a complex heroine worth getting to know.\" (</b><b><i>Publishers Weekly</i></b><b>)</b></p>"; 
